OL,3,CTriathlete could have bled to death
OL,4,Cbefore treatment for rare illness
OL,6,FJersey international triathlete Ollie
OL,7,FTurner says he could have died had he
OL,8,Fnot sought treatment for a rare
OL,9,Fillness.
OL,11,FNow based in Cardiff, Ollie, 26, was
OL,12,Ffound to have immune thrombocytopenic
OL,13,Fpurpura (ITP), meaning he had a very
OL,14,Flow number of platelets in his blood.
OL,16,FHe was encouraged to go to a doctor's
OL,17,Fappointment by his girlfriend,
OL,18,FGeorgia, after developing bruises and
OL,19,Ffeeling fatigued following a training
OL,20,Fcamp earlier this year.
