OL,3,CTriathlete could have bled to death
OL,4,Cbefore treatment for rare illness
OL,6,FHe said: "I wouldn't have bothered
OL,7,Fbecause I wouldn't have deemed myself
OL,8,Fneeding it. I didn't want to take the
OL,9,Fresources because I didn't feel like
OL,10,Fit was warranted but then, what do I
OL,11,Fknow about medicine?
OL,13,F"If I'd fallen off my bike, I'd have
OL,14,Fprobably not even been here because
OL,15,Fthey wouldn't have operated on me
OL,16,Fbecause I wouldn't have had enough
OL,17,Fplatelets.
OL,19,F"They'd have just refused me the
OL,20,Fsurgery, so thank you to her."
