OL,3,CTriathlete could have bled to death
OL,4,Cbefore treatment for rare illness
OL,6,FNow back in training following
OL,7,Ftreatment, Ollie is turning his
OL,8,Fattention to Ironman distance
OL,9,Ftriathlons after the short-course
OL,10,Fevent was dropped from next year's
OL,11,FCommonwealth Games in Glasgow.
OL,13,FOllie finished 26th in the short
OL,14,Fcourse triathlon at his first
OL,15,FCommonwealth Games on Australia's Gold
OL,16,FCoast in 2018 before jumping to 15th
OL,17,Fwhen Birmingham played host in 2022.
