OL,3,CTriathlete could have bled to death
OL,4,Cbefore treatment for rare illness
OL,6,FSpeaking about the switch in focus,
OL,7,FOllie said it was really "deflating
OL,8,Fand demotivating" when he found out
OL,9,Fthe event was out of the 2026 Games.
OL,11,FHe explained: "I had this grand plan
OL,12,Fthat I wanted to go to the 2026
OL,13,FCommonwealth Games, finish my short-
OL,14,Fcourse career and I was aiming for a
OL,15,Ftop ten. I was wanting to tick off
OL,16,Feach one so yeah, it meant a lot to
OL,17,Fme."
OL,19,FMoving onto new challenges, Ollie
OL,20,Frecently raced in Shanghai, finishing
OL,21,F4th at the Ironman 70.3 race on 25 May.
